Detailed Description

Structure to hold the fields of an Atmel Generic record.

Field Documentation

uint32_t _AtmelGenericRecord::address

The 24-bit address field of the record. Note that the Atmel Generic record only supports 24-bit addresses, despite the additional storage capacity (32 bits) of this variable.

uint16_t _AtmelGenericRecord::data

The 16-bit data field of the record.
